Description: # Pyh2m for Scrapy Pipeline
        
        ------------
        settings.py:
        
        ```python
        ...
        # pyh2m settings for crawler project
        RAW_TEXT = True  # raw text or markdown text
        HTML_DICT_NAME = "html"        # item["html"]
        MARK_DICT_NAME = "markdown"    # item["markdown"]
        ...
        ```
        
